---
title: BBQ Chicken Loaded Wedges with black beans and melted cheddar cheese
description: These aren't called loaded wedges for nothing. Topped with black beans, BBQ chicken, cheese and veg, this dish is smoky, spicy and choc-a-block with an array of amazing ingredients.
